name: MD-400D Marlin 0.6 nozzle (Left)
machine_start_gcode:
G28 ; home all axes 
M420 S1;
M117 ; Purge extruder
G92 E0 ; reset extruder
G1 Z1.0 F1200 ; move z up little to prevent scratching of surface
G1 E2 F200;
G92 E0 
G1 X54 Y20 Z0.3 F3000
G1 X4 Y20 Z0.3 F500.0 E5 
G1 X4 Y70.0 Z0.3 F500.0 E10 
G1 X4 Y70.0 Z0.4 F3000.0 
G1 X4 Y20 Z0.4 F500.0 E15 
G1 X54 Y20 Z0.4 F500.0 E20
G92 E0
G1 Z5 E15 F200
G92 E0
G1 Z10 F1500 
G4 S2
G1 Z15 F1500
machine_end_gcode:
G91; relative positioning
G1 Z1.0 F3000 ; move z up little to prevent scratching of print
G90; absolute positioning
G28 X F1000 ; prepare for part removal
M104 S0; turn off extruder
M140 S0 ; turn off bed
M84 ; disable motors
M106 S0 ; turn off fan
